data.description:
Great investment property, with potential of added living space in the home. 

3 Bedroom & 1 bathroom bungalow style home, close to the center of town offering an unfinished attic space perfect for expanding the homes livable areas. Covered front porch, perfect for late evenings out. 
Large 24x28 Detached 2 car garage, perfect for parking and extra storage. 

Home inspection completed, foundation repairs recommended and termite inspection. Home sold as-is and reports can be emailed to agent upon request due to size of report not being able to be uploaded.
